item.title: CVE-2022-27669|2024-08-03T05:33:00.326Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20netweaver%20application%20server%20for%20java
item.description: An unauthenticated user can use functions of XML Data Archiving Service of SAP NetWeaver Application Server for Java - version 7.50, to which access should be restricted. This may result in an escalation of privileges.
